<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hardiment" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hardiment,</orth> boldness, bold exploit: <cit><quote>changing h. with great Glendower,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.101" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 3, 101</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thus popped Paris in his h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 5, 28</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>like h. Posthumus hath to Cymbeline performed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 5.4.75" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 4, 75</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>